# Normalize line endings on commit. Stops the recurring CRLF/LF churn that
# was bloating Phase J-K diffs (style.css had +410 noise lines for 0 real
# changes on 2026-05-15). Added 2026-05-18.

* text=auto eol=lf

# Explicit binary types — never normalize.
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
*.ico binary
*.pdf binary
*.zip binary
*.woff binary
*.woff2 binary
